manifest.description: This file contains the target. This is the dataset that you will use to train your model.

Shows the submission format for this competition, with the ‘ID’ column containing all client IDs and date for the test set and the clicks column containing your forecasts for the number of clicks. The order of the rows does not matter, but name of the item ID needs to be correct.
